1
00:00:09,479 --> 00:00:10,639
I like this one.

2
00:00:10,919 --> 00:00:11,639
What do you think?

3
00:00:14,960 --> 00:00:15,720
What do you think?

4
00:00:18,639 --> 00:00:20,159
I think it's pretty.

5
00:00:24,120 --> 00:00:24,879
What do you think?

6
00:00:25,960 --> 00:00:27,199
If you like it,

7
00:00:27,199 --> 00:00:28,039
you can try it on inside.

8
00:00:28,039 --> 00:00:28,920
There's a fitting room.

9
00:00:29,479 --> 00:00:30,199
Sure.

10
00:00:38,440 --> 00:00:41,599
Young Master Yan, why did you ask me that?

11
00:00:42,080 --> 00:00:43,400
If I don't marry her,

12
00:00:44,239 --> 00:00:45,440
will you be with me?

13
00:00:58,640 --> 00:01:00,360
Is this really for me?

14
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:07,599
Did you make this yourself?

15
00:01:08,679 --> 00:01:10,080
Chengyan doesn't want to eat the nutrient meal.

16
00:01:10,080 --> 00:01:11,280
I'll make him something else.

17
00:01:11,519 --> 00:01:13,560
I can't let him go hungry all the time.

18
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:15,399
I want a sandwich.

19
00:01:16,440 --> 00:01:17,640
Okay, I'll make it right away.

20
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:19,080
I think this one is good.

21
00:01:19,599 --> 00:01:20,480
What do you think?

22
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:43,560
Wanqing, what's wrong?

23
00:01:44,679 --> 00:01:45,920
Is it because of my brother?

24
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,720
He doesn't have to marry me,

25
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:55,840
but I don't understand why he lied to me.

26
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:58,599
But your wedding is about to take place.

27
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:01,239
What exactly went wrong?

28
00:02:04,959 --> 00:02:07,119
I'm the daughter of the Xia family.

29
00:02:07,839 --> 00:02:09,880
Can't I compare to a little caregiver?

30
00:02:12,439 --> 00:02:13,679
Because of Xiaoxue,

31
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:16,719
I've tried very hard

32
00:02:16,719 --> 00:02:18,119
to win your brother's affection.

33
00:02:19,719 --> 00:02:21,119
I've done more for your family

34
00:02:21,119 --> 00:02:23,920
than I ever did for the Xia family.

35
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:28,800
But your brother just can't see it.

36
00:02:30,439 --> 00:02:32,360
He only sees Ji Xiaoxue.

37
00:02:32,999 --> 00:02:34,480
Even the ring he gave me

38
00:02:34,480 --> 00:02:36,320
was meant for Ji Xiaoxue.

39
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:39,519
The wedding dress we picked

40
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:41,760
has to be one Ji Xiaoxue would like.

41
00:02:43,679 --> 00:02:45,640
Am I really that unlikable?

42
00:02:46,679 --> 00:02:47,760
Am I really not good enough

43
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:49,399
to be part of the Gu family?

44
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:51,839
In my heart,

45
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:55,160
you're always the best.

46
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:58,040
My brother doesn't cherish you.

47
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:59,320
That's his loss.

48
00:03:05,119 --> 00:03:06,160
You still have me.

49
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:17,999
Are you crazy?

50
00:04:00,880 --> 00:04:01,760
Xiaoxue,

51
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:03,439
do you have a boyfriend?

52
00:04:05,399 --> 00:04:06,200
Boyfriend?

53
00:04:08,999 --> 00:04:10,480
I... I don't have one.

54
00:04:14,879 --> 00:04:15,759
Take this.

55
00:04:15,999 --> 00:04:16,920
What's this?

56
00:04:17,439 --> 00:04:18,439
There's some money in here.

57
00:04:18,840 --> 00:04:20,280
It should be enough for you to spend a long time.

58
00:04:20,999 --> 00:04:22,360
Spend it however you want.

59
00:04:24,679 --> 00:04:26,800
Mr. Gu, I can't take this money.

60
00:04:27,079 --> 00:04:28,160
I am short of money,

61
00:04:28,199 --> 00:04:29,559
but every penny I earn

62
00:04:29,559 --> 00:04:31,280
is the result of my own hard work.

63
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,199
You've got it wrong.

64
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:34,800
I just feel that

65
00:04:35,439 --> 00:04:37,119
you remind me of an old friend of mine.

66
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,879
I miss her very much.

67
00:04:41,119 --> 00:04:43,439
Then you can give this money to your friend.

68
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:44,559
You don't have to give it to me.

69
00:04:44,879 --> 00:04:46,239
If I tell you to take it, just take it.

70
00:04:46,639 --> 00:04:47,559
You can spend it,

71
00:04:47,759 --> 00:04:48,800
or you can choose not to spend it.

72
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:50,879
You can also take this money now,

73
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:51,840
and leave immediately.

74
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:53,639
Go do whatever you want to do.

75
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:55,920
You don't need to feel any pressure.

76
00:04:56,999 --> 00:04:58,079
Just consider this money

77
00:04:58,960 --> 00:04:59,879
as a debt I owe you.

78
00:05:02,319 --> 00:05:02,840
I...

79
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:03,559
Take it.

80
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:06,239
Or I'll fire you right now.

81
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,400
Let's stop here for today.

82
00:05:08,999 --> 00:05:10,559
Just pretend nothing happened.

83
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:37,480
Young Master Jing, why are you here?

84
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,840
Did my uncle talk to you today?

85
00:05:41,119 --> 00:05:42,160
No, he didn't.

86
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:52,119
Why are you lying to me?

87
00:06:02,679 --> 00:06:04,199
Why are you lying to me?

88
00:06:05,639 --> 00:06:07,239
I've given you two chances.

89
00:06:08,239 --> 00:06:10,160
Yesterday, you said you were in the garden with my brother,

90
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:11,960
but I found your brooch

91
00:06:12,759 --> 00:06:14,280
in the cellar.

92
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:19,079
Today, you were clearly here

93
00:06:19,079 --> 00:06:20,360
talking with my uncle for so long,

94
00:06:21,439 --> 00:06:22,559
but you said you didn't see him.

95
00:06:24,119 --> 00:06:25,439
Why are you lying to me?

96
00:06:26,319 --> 00:06:28,879
It's... It's because they won't let me say anything.

97
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:31,160
They said if I told,

98
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,319
they would kick me out.

99
00:06:32,319 --> 00:06:33,360
Then what did you do?

100
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,600
They wouldn't let you talk.

101
00:06:34,759 --> 00:06:35,960
I didn't do anything.

102
00:06:38,199 --> 00:06:38,920
They...

103
00:06:40,520 --> 00:06:42,960
They said they like me.

104
00:06:44,879 --> 00:06:45,879
Then who do you like?

105
00:06:45,960 --> 00:06:46,720
You.

106
00:06:51,559 --> 00:06:54,280
Young Master Jing, I came here because of you.

107
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,040
Young Master Yan treated me like this,

108
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:57,079
but I didn't leave.

109
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:58,239
It's also because of you.

110
00:06:59,119 --> 00:07:00,600
I'm afraid they'll fire me,

111
00:07:01,639 --> 00:07:02,639
also because of you.

112
00:08:06,119 --> 00:08:06,800
Remember,

113
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,600
you'll always be mine.

114
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:12,480
You can only listen to me.

115
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,719
That's it for today's meeting.

116
00:08:30,839 --> 00:08:31,679
Meeting adjourned.

117
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:45,959
Wanqing,

118
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,280
do you need me to take you home?

119
00:08:49,079 --> 00:08:49,880
No, thanks.

120
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,640
If you're free,

121
00:08:55,479 --> 00:08:57,079
could you come with me to a bridal shop?

122
00:09:12,920 --> 00:09:13,640
How do you like it?

123
00:09:14,719 --> 00:09:15,439
It's nice,

124
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:18,040
but I think it's a bit too plain for you.

125
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:19,920
I think

126
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:21,959
this one suits you better.

127
00:09:35,199 --> 00:09:37,679
Xiaoxue, do you have plans later?

128
00:09:37,959 --> 00:09:39,079
I need to talk to you about something.

129
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,920
I'm going to give Young Master Yan a facial treatment.

130
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:46,280
Sir, do you need anything?
